<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 03:14:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾总统在中国威胁分裂主义后表示独裁是“邪恶的”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/autocracy-is-evil-taiwan-president-says-after-china-threatens-death-separatism-2024-06-24/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周一在中国威胁要对“顽固”台独分裂分子判处死刑后表示，民主不是犯罪，独裁才是真正的“罪恶”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/autocracy-is-evil-taiwan-president-says-after-china-threatens-death-separatism-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>据中国官方媒体报道，中国希望欧盟在 7 月 4 日之前取消对电动汽车的电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-wants-eu-scrap-ev-tariffs-evs-by-july-4-chinese-state-media-reports-2024-06-24/</link><description>据中国官方媒体《环球时报》报道，在双方同意举行新的贸易谈判后，北京希望欧盟在 7 月 4 日之前取消对中国电动汽车的初步关税。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-wants-eu-scrap-ev-tariffs-evs-by-july-4-chinese-state-media-reports-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院推迟中国佳兆业集团清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-kaisa-group-liquidation-petition-adjourned-by-hong-kong-court-2024-06-24/</link><description>周一，香港一家法院将寻求佳兆业集团清算的请愿书的听证会推迟至 8 月 12 日，这让这家陷入困境的中国开发商在实施债务重组计划时得到了一些喘息的机会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 02:12:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-kaisa-group-liquidation-petition-adjourned-by-hong-kong-court-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>通胀数据公布前美元持稳；日元徘徊在160附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-ahead-inflation-reading-yen-teeters-toward-160-2024-06-24/</link><description>美元周一持稳，因交易员期待美国通胀路径的新线索，这可能会影响利率，而日本当局的言论并没有阻止日元跌势回到160整数关口。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 01:42:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-ahead-inflation-reading-yen-teeters-toward-160-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>通胀和政治因素凸显亚洲股市低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-24/</link><description>在美国价格数据倒计时期间，亚洲股市低迷。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 00:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国将军：俄罗斯朝鲜防务协议可能与中国产生摩擦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russias-north-korea-defense-deal-could-create-friction-with-china-us-general-2024-06-23/</link><description>美国高级军官周日表示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京与朝鲜的共同防御协议有可能与中国产生摩擦，中国长期以来一直是这个隐居国家的主要盟友。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 22:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russias-north-korea-defense-deal-could-create-friction-with-china-us-general-2024-06-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：日元交易员关注日本央行会议纪要，中国关注反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-23/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 21:49:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-23/</guid></item><item><title>达赖喇嘛抵达纽约治病</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/dalai-lama-arrives-new-york-trip-medical-treatment-2024-06-23/</link><description>藏传佛教流亡精神领袖达赖喇嘛于周日抵达纽约，接受膝盖治疗，受到数百名欢呼雀跃、高呼口号的支持者的欢迎。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 18:13:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/dalai-lama-arrives-new-york-trip-medical-treatment-2024-06-23/</guid></item><item><title>南非橄榄球协会和中国在巴黎预订国际七人榄球赛席位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/rugby-china-book-place-womens-rugby-sevens-paris-2024-2024-06-23/</link><description>周日在摩纳哥举行的复活赛资格赛决赛中，南非队以 14-5 战胜英国队，获得巴黎奥运会男子七人制橄榄球比赛的参赛资格。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 16:55:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/rugby-china-book-place-womens-rugby-sevens-paris-2024-2024-06-23/</guid></item><item><title>德国经济部长敦促中国放弃煤电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/german-minister-says-china-indispensable-achieve-climate-goals-2024-06-23/</link><description>德国经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克周日表示，中国对于实现全球气候目标不可或缺，必须找到煤炭的安全替代品，2023年煤炭占中国电力供应的近60%。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 07:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/german-minister-says-china-indispensable-achieve-climate-goals-2024-06-23/</guid></item><item><title>马科斯总统表示菲律宾无意挑起战争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-not-business-instigating-wars-says-president-marcos-2024-06-23/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周日表示，在与中国的海上对抗不断升级的情况下，菲律宾不会挑起战争，将始终致力于和平解决争端。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 03:26:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-not-business-instigating-wars-says-president-marcos-2024-06-23/</guid></item><item><title>台湾兵棋尽可能模拟战斗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-war-games-mimic-combat-closely-possible-2024-06-23/</link><description>一位不愿透露姓名的台湾防务高级官员表示，迫切需要重新考虑演习的进行方式。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 01:08:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-war-games-mimic-combat-closely-possible-2024-06-23/</guid></item><item><title>胡尔卡奇击败兹维列夫，与辛纳争夺哈雷决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/hurkacz-downs-zverev-set-up-halle-final-with-sinner-2024-06-22/</link><description>休伯特·胡尔卡茨在发球局上几乎势不可挡，轰出 17 个 ace 球并挽救了 4 个破发点，击败了本月在法国公开赛上获得亚军的亚历山大·兹维列夫。</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 15:38:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/hurkacz-downs-zverev-set-up-halle-final-with-sinner-2024-06-22/</guid></item><item><title>梵蒂冈根据北京协议任命中国杭州主教</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/vatican-names-chinas-hangzhou-bishop-via-accord-with-beijing-2024-06-22/</link><description>梵蒂冈周六表示，教皇方济各已任命朱塞佩·杨永强为中国东部浙江省省会杭州主教，以努力加强与北京的关系。</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 13:18:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/vatican-names-chinas-hangzhou-bishop-via-accord-with-beijing-2024-06-22/</guid></item><item><title>美国东亚特使表示南海局势深感担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-east-asia-envoy-says-south-china-sea-situation-deeply-concerning-2024-06-22/</link><description>美国负责东亚和太平洋事务的助理国务卿丹尼尔·克里滕布林克周六表示，南海局势令人深感担忧，并表示中国最近在争议航道上的行动“严重破坏了稳定”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 12:40:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-east-asia-envoy-says-south-china-sea-situation-deeply-concerning-2024-06-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>